endar doesn’t look right.'=>'我的日记看上去不对劲。','Here’s an overview of %s and what they mean.'=>'这里有 %s 预览和解释','Create Eventbrite tickets and events right from your WordPress dashboard.'=>'直接从您的 WordPress 仪表板创建 Eventbrite 门票和活动。','Enable 3rd party event submissions.'=>'启用第 3 方事件提交。','Allow users to search for events by category, tag, venue, organizer, day of the week, time of day, and price.'=>'允许用户按类别、标签、地点、组织者、星期几、一天中的时间和价格搜索活动。','Email marketing to promote your events'=>'电子邮件营销以宣传您的活动','Collect RSVPs and sell tickets'=>'收集回复并出售门票','Import events from Meetup, Eventbrite, iCal, Google Calendar, and more.'=>'从 Meetup、Eventbrite、iCal、Google 日历等导入活动。','The #1 calendar for WordPress'=>'WordPress 排名第一的日历','There are a few %s to resolve and prevent 404 errors.'=>'有几个 %s 可以解决和防止 404 错误。','I keep getting “Page Not Found” on events.'=>'我不断收到有关事件的“页面未找到”。','%s and other common installation issues.'=>'%s 和其他常见的安装问题。','I installed the calendar and it crashed my site.'=>'我安装了日历，它使我的网站崩溃了。','This can happen when other plugins try to improve performance. %s.'=>'当其他插件试图提高性能时，可能会发生这种情况。 %s。','Common Error Messages'=>'普通错误信息','Check for updates'=>'检查更新','It\'s important to use the most recent versions of our plugins so that you have access to the latest features, bug fixes, and security updates. Plugin functionality can be comprimised if your site is running outdated or mis-matched versions.'=>'使用我们插件的最新版本非常重要，这样您就可以访问最新的功能、错误修复和安全更新。如果您的网站运行的是过时或不匹配的版本，则插件功能可能会受到影响。','Plugin(s) are out of date'=>'插件已过期','Enter a custom API key'=>'输入自己的 API 密钥。','The Events Calendar comes with an API key for basic maps functionality. If you’d like to use more advanced features like custom map pins, dynamic map loads, or Events Calendar Pro\'s Location Search and advanced Map View, you’ll need to get your own Google Maps API key and add it to Events > Settings > Integrations'=>'The Events Calendar 附带了一个用于基本地图功能的API密钥。如果您想使用更高级的功能，如自定义地图图钉或动态地图加载，您需要使用自己的Google Maps API密钥，并添加到活动>设置>集成','Manage your licenses